SUMMARY:Ignite's 50th Anniversary Storytelling Event @ Benaroya Hall!
DESCRIPTION:🔥 Ignite Seattle #50 — 20 Years\, 50 Shows\, Thousands of Sparks! 🔥\nTuesday\, March 10\, 2026 • 6:00 PM\nBenaroya Hall • Seattle\, WA \nFifty shows. Two decades of ideas. Thousands of sparks of inspiration. Join us for a milestone celebration as Ignite Seattle takes over the historic Benaroya Hall for its 50th Anniversary Storytelling Show — a once-in-a-generation night of curiosity\, courage\, and connection. \nIgnite is where everyday voices take the spotlight and extraordinary stories come alive. Expect rapid-fire storytelling from community members across Seattle — each speaker gets exactly 5 minutes and 20 slides that auto-advance every 15 seconds to share something they care about passionately\, humorously\, or profoundly. \nFrom big ideas to personal revelations\, surprising wisdom to delightful detours\, this special anniversary edition brings the energy of Ignite like you’ve never seen it — live onstage in one of the city’s most iconic performance venues. Whether you’re a longtime fan or curious newcomer\, this night will leave you inspired\, entertained\, and part of something uniquely Seattle.
URL:https://www.geekwire.com/calendar-event/ignites-50th-anniversary-storytelling-event-benaroya-hall/
LOCATION:Benaroya Hall\, 200 University Street\, Seattle\, WA\, 98101\, United States
CATEGORIES:Arts
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://cdn.geekwire.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/zwzgcdp26vqkx7aqvrqg.jpg
