SUMMARY:GTM IN THE AI ERA
DESCRIPTION:​GTM in the AI Era: People\, Stack\, and What’s Actually Working \n​Join us at AI House for an off-the-record style\, high-signal conversation on how AI is reshaping go-to-market. This is a moderated panel\, built for real dialogue and practical takeaways\, not pitches or demos. \n​We’ll unpack three angles leaders are navigating right now: \n​People & AI: hiring trends\, AI literacy\, and recruiting impact \n​GTM Foundations + Tech Stack: what must be true before layering AI into your GTM motion \n​Market Trends & Lessons Learned: what’s working\, what isn’t\, and where teams are getting surprised \n​Date: March 18\nTime: 4:30–6:30 PM (networking before and after the panel)\nLocation: AI House\nFormat: 35–45 minute moderated panel + networking \n​Who it’s for: CROs\, VPs/Directors of Sales\, Growth leaders\, Founders\, and select Investors. \n​Capacity is limited. If this is your world\, you’ll leave with sharper perspective\, clearer language\, and a more grounded view of what “AI-ready GTM” actually looks like.
