SUMMARY:SEATTLE FOUNDER CAPITAL SUMMIT
DESCRIPTION:Startup & Scaleup Funding Access\n​Hosted by Core Team & CT Capital\n​🗓️ March 25–26 @ SURF Incubator \n​For founders ready to explore funding solutions and gain real traction. \n​FOR-PROFITS & NON-PROFITS WELCOMED \n​Attendees will gain access to structured funding pathways typically ranging from $250K to $1M\, depending on stage and business readiness\, along with integration into a complete ecosystem designed to support traction and long-term growth. 💰 🤝 💼 \n—- \nFounders Showcase \n​Registration opens on March 3rd \n​The first 20 approved companies will present live before an executive review panel. Selected companies will receive priority capital evaluation\, strategic advisor alignment\, and accelerated incubation consideration. \n​Spots are limited to ensure meaningful engagement. \n—- \nWhether you are at the ideation stage\, pre-revenue\, or scaling — spanning technology\, consumer products\, services\, sustainability\, and mission-driven ventures — you will connect with experienced operators\, capital structuring teams\, revenue channels\, acquisition pathways\, and in-person incubator support all at one event. 🚀 \n​Enjoy real conversations focused on funding\, revenue\, and long-term stability. \n​Food and beverages are available. 🍹 \n—– \nAll event proceeds support our nonprofit partners\, Cherry Willow Initiative and ISDI\, advancing programs that serve individuals experiencing homelessness and professionals affected by workplace inequities.
