DESCRIPTION:ABOUT \nThursday\, April 9\n8:30 AM – 5:00 PM\nSeattle Colleges – Georgetown Campus\n6737 Corson Ave S. Seattle\, WA \nThe Higher Education Summit: The Impact of AI will bring together academic leaders\, business innovators\, and workforce directors for a one-day\, highly interactive forum focused on preparing students for this new era. The program will combine thought-provoking keynote and panel sessions with outcome-driven small-group discussions. Each breakout will generate actionable strategies and contribute to a shared AI in Higher Education Playbook—a roadmap for institutional readiness\, responsible integration\, and future workforce alignment. Free parking available.
